title: Curcumin C3 Power 525mg
description:
About products:-

Curcumin C3 Power is a patented and clinically evaluated Bio-protectant composition of three Curcuminoids in a convenient form that is better absorbed in the body. Curcuminoids have traditionally been used in Ayurveda in the management of painful conditions from sore throats to arthritis.

Fitness, wellness and a healthy life - offered to you through one of nature’s greatest gifts to mankind – Curcuminoids. Turmeric may be the most effective nutritional supplement in nature and Curcuminoids, natural compounds derived from turmeric roots, inhibit NF-kB, the ‘master switch’ for inflammation. Curcuminoids are valued for their antioxidant and anti-inflammatory benefits for holistic health and wellness management.

Most degenerative diseases are driven by underlying chronic sub-clinical inflammation. While it was earlier believed that inflammation represents the healing process, research in this area has revealed that when inflammation becomes chronic, it manifests itself as a disease condition. It has been well researched that the use of natural products such as Curcuminoids would be effective and safe to manage inflammation.

Key Benefits:

Curcumin C3 Complex® is the #1 clinically studied and evaluated curcumin brand in the market today, with over 45+ clinical studies to establish its efficacy.
  • Natural Herbal antioxidant supplement
  • Supports overall wellness and good health
  • Helps manage recurrence of frequent cold and viral infections
  • Offers support from stress related health conditions
  • Most potent Anti-oxidant
  • Clinically tested and proven
  • Curcumin may help delay aging and fight age-related chronic conditions

Suggested Usage:

One tablet in morning and one at night after meals with water or warm milk.

Ingredients:

Curcumin C3 Complex®: The #1 clinically studied, evaluated and patented curcumin brand on the market today, with over 45+ clinical studies to establish its efficacy. It is obtained from the dried rhizomes of Curcuma longa, and standardized for minimum 95% Curcuminoids.The name C3 Complex has reference to its three main chemical compounds - Curcumin, Demethoxycurcumin (DMC) and Bisdemethoxycurcumin (BDMC) - collectively known as Curcuminoids. It’s not just Curcumin but the Curcuminoids.Curcumin C3 Complex® is the only Curcumin in the market that has been reviewed and acknowledged by the USFDA for its GRAS status.

BioPerine®BioPerine® is obtained from the dried fruits of Piper nigrum (black pepper) and is standardized form of Piperine. BioPerine® has been used as a #bioavailability enhancer.
